WorkItem.Description: Agility showing very high survivability contributions to the point that 1 point of Agility is worth 1.5 points of Stamina. The default survivabilty scale of 1.0 shows Agility being worth nearly 4 times as much on RSV charts. I understand that the chart is to be taken with a grain of salt but it seems to skew the upgrade list a little as well. Here's my sub-par pre-pre-heroic geared warrior has a sample file.

Comments.Message: Fury isn't Cataclysm ready at all, don't use Rawr for Fury yet. The only changes I have done for it were to keep it from flat out breaking.
